entries.femaleVariant: If you ever need any help, let me know.
If you ever need help with something, just give me a holler.
Let's not get too cocky, all right?
The life of a merc's got its ups and downs.
Next time it'll be me pulling you out of some colossal fuck-up.
So long as I got the eddies on me, am I right?
You did Regina and I both a favor – not like we're about to forget that anytime soon.
I met your brother.
So, ran into Big Pete. You both got a wicked talent for finding trouble.
Yeah, told me you helped him out. Might put you as emergency contact for the whole fam.
Who knows when my mom or pop will need a hand in a hurry.
Sure, think I can even toss in a family discount.
How's the arm?
V, hey! C'mere, let's talk!
[Drink] Could use a drink first.
Sure, but tongue's feelin' a bit stiff. Toss one back first?
With you, anytime.
Hahaha! Ain't wrong!
How's the arm holdin' up?
Awww, V, such a tender soul you are.
C'mon, Tiny, bein' serious.
Well, after payin' you and Regina your due, I still had eddies in the bank for this bad boy.
So, yeah – I'd say the arm's fine.
